ce rock]] *[[Psychedelic rock]] **[[Acid rock]] **[[Freakbeat]] **[[Neo-psychedelia]] **[[Raga rock]] *[[Punk rock]] **[[Anarcho punk]] ***[[Crust punk]] ****[[D-beat]] **[[Art punk]] **[[Christian punk]] **[[Deathrock]] **[[Digital hardcore]] **[[Folk punk]] ***[[Celtic punk]] ***[[Cowpunk]] ***[[Gypsy punk]] **[[Garage punk (fusion genre)|Garage punk]] **[[Grindcore]] ***[[Crustgrind]] ***[[Noisegrind]] ***[[Goregrind]] **[[Hardcore punk]] ***[[Post-hardcore]] ****[[Emo]] *****[[Emo pop]] *****[[Screamo]] ***[[Thrashcore]] ***[[Crossover thrash]] ***[[Powerviolence]] ***[[Street punk]] **[[Horror punk]] **[[Pop punk]] ***[[Neon pop]] **[[Nazi punk]] **[[Psychobilly]] **[[Riot grrrl]] **[[Ska punk]] **[[Skate punk]] *[[Rap rock]] **[[Rapcore]] *[[Eric_Lewis_(pianist)#Later_career_and_"Rockjazz"|Rockjazz]] *[[Rock and roll]] *[[Southern rock]] *[[Stoner rock]] *[[Sufi rock]] *[[Surf rock]] *[[Visual kei]] **[[Nagoya kei]] *[[Worldbeat]] }}
