{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2018}}
The '''Robert Award for Best Danish Television Series''' ({{lang-da|Robert Prisen for årets danske tv-serie}}) is one of the merit awards presented by the [[Danish Film Academy]] at the annual [[Robert Awards]] ceremony. The award has been handed out since 2013.

== Honorees ==

=== 2010s ===
* 2013: ''[[The Killing (Danish TV series)|Forbrydelsen 3]]'' – [[Mikkel Serup]]
* 2014: ''[[Borgen (TV series)|Borgen III]]'' – [[Charlotte Sieling]]
* 2015: ''[[The Legacy (TV series)|The Legacy]]'' – [[Pernilla August]]
